{"tid":1370521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)今日去元朗既兄弟！幫手捉住依幾隻鬼！","createTime":"2019-07-27T04:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:39:02.000Z","uid":283968,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fca97f90392e911439b6864c0aa014dea192c40f","tid":1370521,"uid":283968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:30:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdLCfiL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdLCfiL.png&h=4483bf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係依幾隻鬼，大家一齊<span style=\"color: red;\">下載 POKEMONGO</span> 幫手捉，天氣好熱記得<span style=\"color: red;\">帶長傘</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">飲多啲水</span>，同埋元朗鄉村地方啲路好難行，<span style=\"color: red;\">帶返把拐扙</span>都好合理！<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>[外國勢力]我諗到個唔知掂唔掂既行動，依次真係揾美國幫手！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369719\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369719</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n(幫手刷點擊賺廣告費)POKEMONGO既攻略影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLP26LrCV47uf71O7MAGCFFAjsbyl7VOpq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLP26LrCV47uf71O7MAGCFFAjsbyl7VOpq&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=821ee733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLP26LrCV47uf71O7MAGCFFAjsbyl7VOpq</a><br />\n<br />\n每日都會公佈返<span style=\"color: red;\">觀看次數</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">營利</span>既數據，買咗既<span style=\"color: red;\">物資</span>都會有收據同埋講放咗係邊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d10127eaf03316a696d06bd0370c77c7a3c8dca2","tid":1370521,"uid":216789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:31:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1c710cfe711ba2c249c80cde3dbf9ba6ca385623","tid":1370521,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/yrkycbu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyrkycbu.png&h=62fcbf80&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b79a125ef223f9465be69c1493bdf8d978c3273","tid":1370521,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～！<br />\n<br />\n大家今日出街一定要帶哨子，長遮！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1370461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1370461</a>"},{"pid":"f9fd730a8233ead62b14f7785f8b767b786e8d0e","tid":1370521,"uid":157857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b460200077fdcecdea2f3d3e5fb28166af0cccf","tid":1370521,"uid":157857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}